
<!doctype html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>STE application acknowledgement email (For Full-time / Part-time/ Other – Government agency)</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Montserrat:300,400,500,700" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body style="font-family: 'Poppins' , sans-serif; font-size:14px;color:#302c2b; line-height:2;">
    <div class="rt-tb-scrl">
        <div class="col-md-12">
            <p>Dear Sir / Madam,</p>
            <p>This is with reference to the application received for <b>@Model.PersonName</b> for the post of <b>@Model.DesignationName (@Model.TypeofAppointment)</b> from <b>@Model.AppointmentStartDate</b> to <b>@Model.AppointmentEndDate</b> under the Project no: <b>@Model.ProjectNumber</b> with the <b>@Model.Paytype of Rs. @Model.BasicPay /- per month</b> is under Process.</p>
            <p>The following will be the next steps from our end.</p>
            <p>
                @if (Model.TypeofAppointment == "Selection")
                {
                    <ol type="1">
                        <li>Commitment booking</li>
                        <li>Dean IC&SR approval</li>
                        <li>Offer Release</li>
                    </ol>
                }
                else
                {
                    <ol type="1">
                        <li>Commitment booking</li>
                        <li>Committee approval</li>
                        <li>Offer Release</li>
                    </ol>
                }
            </p>
            <p>@*The normal turnaround time to release the offer letter is 7 working days from the receipt of this email.*@</p>
            <p>For any queries, kindly send an email to <a href="mailto:icsrrecruitment1@imail.iitm.ac.in" target="_blank"> icsrrecruitment1@imail.iitm.ac.in </a>/<a href="mailto:icsrrecruitment@iitm.ac.in" target="_blank"> icsrrecruitment@iitm.ac.in</a> and we will get back to you at the earliest.</p>
            <p>Thanks and Regards,</p>
            <p style="margin-top:0px;">
                @Model.DAName<br>
                Project Recruitment<br>
                Centre for IC&SR<br>
                IIT Madras<br>
                *This is a system generated email.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
